{
  "name": "code-review",
  "version": "0.2.0",
  "min_engine_version": "1.0.0",
  "max_depth": 6,
  "_note": "The full custody pipeline plus the mental-model gates, wired as engine phases: preflight fanout(4 cluster branches: adherence[spec-solves-issue||plan-implements-spec||code-implements-plan]->adherence-rollup, mm-compliance[gather->judge], consistency[docs||tests]->consistency-rollup, security[gather->judge]) -> join-preflight -> preflight-gate -> overview(+risk) -> review fanout(5 dims) -> join -> triage -> fix -> post-fix fanout[context || mm-updater->mm-gate] -> join -> mrp -> done. Each phase pairs the generic `evidence-present` form check with a deterministic per-phase gate: preflight (a 4-cluster nested fanout joined under preflight-gate, whose conclude-preflight runs a deterministic block-gaps/warn-extras rollup over the issue->spec->plan->code chain + mm-compliance, posts one consolidated comment, and halts via on_blocked:halt until /override), overview (schema + cohort-partition + a deterministic `conclude-overview` risk scorer porting score.js/diffusion.js that owns the authoritative band and halts only on a garbled/unknown run; the agent's risk_band is an advisory hint), the 5 review dims (schema + findings-anchored + publish-review; the fanout's params.status_note flags request-changes legs in the status header), triage (schema + conclude-triage), fix (schema + conclude-fix). The post-fix fanout runs context (schema-valid only, advisory -- a fanout leg runs NO conclude hook, so conclude-context.py is unused here) in PARALLEL with mm-updater (evidence-present + mm-questions-present; a gh-aw create-pull-request safe-output opens an [mm] PR when mm_changed, the mm-gate then holds for a human /mm-answer, else the empty gate auto-skips); the join waits for both before mrp (schema + conclude-mrp + a deterministic acceptance_plan: engine inputs[] deliver prior-phase evidence, per-cohort bands are re-derived via the shared _risk_score, and the custody-shaped pack is emitted as the merge-readiness-pack artifact). Remaining v1 simplifications to improve per-phase later: /fix is suggest-only (no push/PR/comment write-actions), and review findings are not yet posted as inline PR comments. Agent workflows live in .github/workflows/.",
  "triggers": [
    { "on": "issue_comment", "comment_prefix": "/review", "command": "start" },
    { "on": "issue_comment", "comment_prefix": "/override", "command": "override" },
    { "on": "issue_comment", "comment_prefix": "/mm-answer", "command": "answer" }
  ],
  "states": [
    {
      "id": "preflight",
      "kind": "fanout",
      "label": "pre-flight adherence chain",
      "branches": [
        {
          "id": "adherence",
          "states": [
            {
              "id": "adherence-fanout",
              "kind": "fanout",
              "next": "join-adherence",
              "branches": [
                {
                  "id": "spec-solves-issue",
                  "states": [
                    {
                      "id": "spec-solves-issue-gather",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "spec-solves-issue-agent",
                      "evidence": "spec-solves-issue.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "params": { "require": ["verdict", "examined"] },
                      "checks": [
                        { "run": "evidence-present",           "on_fail": "iterate" },
                        { "run": "spec-solves-issue-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "spec-solves-issue-judge",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "spec-solves-issue-judge-agent",
                      "evidence": "judge.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "inputs": [ { "from": "spec-solves-issue-gather", "as": "gather" } ],
                      "params": { "leg": "spec-solves-issue", "mode": "spec-solves" },
                      "checks": [ { "run": "judge-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "id": "plan-implements-spec",
                  "states": [
                    {
                      "id": "plan-implements-spec-gather",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "plan-implements-spec-agent",
                      "evidence": "plan-implements-spec.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "params": { "require": ["verdict", "examined"] },
                      "checks": [
                        { "run": "evidence-present",   "on_fail": "iterate" },
                        { "run": "plan-spec-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "plan-implements-spec-judge",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "plan-implements-spec-judge-agent",
                      "evidence": "judge.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "inputs": [ { "from": "plan-implements-spec-gather", "as": "gather" } ],
                      "params": { "leg": "plan-implements-spec", "mode": "plan-spec" },
                      "checks": [ { "run": "judge-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "id": "code-implements-plan",
                  "states": [
                    {
                      "id": "code-implements-plan-gather",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "code-implements-plan-agent",
                      "evidence": "code-implements-plan.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "params": { "require": ["verdict", "examined"] },
                      "checks": [
                        { "run": "evidence-present",     "on_fail": "iterate" },
                        { "run": "code-plan-coverage",   "on_fail": "iterate" },
                        { "run": "traces-exist-in-diff", "on_fail": "iterate" }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "code-implements-plan-judge",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "code-implements-plan-judge-agent",
                      "evidence": "judge.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "inputs": [ { "from": "code-implements-plan-gather", "as": "gather" } ],
                      "params": { "leg": "code-implements-plan", "mode": "code-plan" },
                      "checks": [ { "run": "judge-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            { "id": "join-adherence", "kind": "join", "of": "adherence-fanout" },
            {
              "id": "adherence-rollup",
              "kind": "agent",
              "workflow": "adherence-rollup-agent",
              "evidence": "cluster.evidence.schema.json",
              "max_iterations": 2,
              "inputs": [
                { "from": "spec-solves-issue",   "as": "spec-solves-issue" },
                { "from": "plan-implements-spec", "as": "plan-implements-spec" },
                { "from": "code-implements-plan", "as": "code-implements-plan" }
              ],
              "params": { "legs": ["spec-solves-issue", "plan-implements-spec", "code-implements-plan"] },
              "checks": [ { "run": "cluster-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "mm-compliance",
          "states": [
            {
              "id": "mm-compliance-gather",
              "kind": "agent",
              "workflow": "mm-compliance-gate",
              "evidence": "mm-compliance.evidence.schema.json",
              "max_iterations": 2,
              "params": { "require": ["verdict"] },
              "checks": [
                { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "mm-compliance-judge",
              "kind": "agent",
              "workflow": "mm-compliance-judge-agent",
              "evidence": "judge.evidence.schema.json",
              "max_iterations": 2,
              "inputs": [ { "from": "mm-compliance-gather", "as": "gather" } ],
              "params": { "leg": "mm-compliance", "mode": "mm" },
              "checks": [ { "run": "judge-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "consistency",
          "states": [
            {
              "id": "consistency-fanout",
              "kind": "fanout",
              "next": "join-consistency",
              "branches": [
                {
                  "id": "docs-updated-appropriately",
                  "states": [
                    {
                      "id": "docs-updated-appropriately-gather",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "docs-coherence-agent",
                      "evidence": "docs-coherence.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "params": { "require": ["verdict", "examined"] },
                      "checks": [
                        { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" },
                        { "run": "docs-coverage",    "on_fail": "iterate" }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "docs-updated-appropriately-judge",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "docs-updated-appropriately-judge-agent",
                      "evidence": "judge.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "inputs": [ { "from": "docs-updated-appropriately-gather", "as": "gather" } ],
                      "params": { "leg": "docs-updated-appropriately", "mode": "coherence" },
                      "checks": [ { "run": "judge-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "id": "tests-updated-appropriately",
                  "states": [
                    {
                      "id": "tests-updated-appropriately-gather",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "tests-coherence-agent",
                      "evidence": "tests-coherence.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "params": { "require": ["verdict", "examined"] },
                      "checks": [
                        { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" },
                        { "run": "tests-coverage",   "on_fail": "iterate" }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "tests-updated-appropriately-judge",
                      "kind": "agent",
                      "workflow": "tests-updated-appropriately-judge-agent",
                      "evidence": "judge.evidence.schema.json",
                      "max_iterations": 2,
                      "inputs": [ { "from": "tests-updated-appropriately-gather", "as": "gather" } ],
                      "params": { "leg": "tests-updated-appropriately", "mode": "coherence" },
                      "checks": [ { "run": "judge-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            { "id": "join-consistency", "kind": "join", "of": "consistency-fanout" },
            {
              "id": "consistency-rollup",
              "kind": "agent",
              "workflow": "consistency-rollup-agent",
              "evidence": "cluster.evidence.schema.json",
              "max_iterations": 2,
              "inputs": [
                { "from": "docs-updated-appropriately",  "as": "docs-updated-appropriately" },
                { "from": "tests-updated-appropriately", "as": "tests-updated-appropriately" }
              ],
              "params": { "legs": ["docs-updated-appropriately", "tests-updated-appropriately"] },
              "checks": [ { "run": "cluster-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "security",
          "states": [
            {
              "id": "security-gather",
              "kind": "agent",
              "workflow": "security-gather-agent",
              "evidence": "security-gather.evidence.schema.json",
              "max_iterations": 2,
              "checks": [
                { "run": "evidence-present",        "on_fail": "iterate" },
                { "run": "security-gather-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "security-judge",
              "kind": "agent",
              "workflow": "security-judge-agent",
              "evidence": "judge.evidence.schema.json",
              "max_iterations": 2,
              "inputs": [ { "from": "security-gather", "as": "gather" } ],
              "params": { "leg": "security", "mode": "security" },
              "checks": [ { "run": "judge-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" } ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "next": "join-preflight"
    },
    { "id": "join-preflight", "kind": "join", "of": "preflight", "next": "preflight-gate" },
    {
      "id": "preflight-gate",
      "kind": "agent",
      "label": "pre-flight adherence gate",
      "workflow": "preflight-gate-agent",
      "evidence": "preflight-gate.evidence.schema.json",
      "max_iterations": 2,
      "inputs": [
        { "from": "adherence",    "as": "adherence" },
        { "from": "mm-compliance", "as": "mm-compliance" },
        { "from": "consistency",  "as": "consistency" },
        { "from": "security",     "as": "security" }
      ],
      "params": { "legs": ["spec-solves-issue", "plan-implements-spec", "code-implements-plan", "mm-compliance", "docs-updated-appropriately", "tests-updated-appropriately", "security"] },
      "checks": [
        { "run": "preflight-gate-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate"  },
        { "run": "local-review-evidence",   "on_fail": "advisory" }
      ],
      "conclude": "conclude-preflight",
      "on_blocked": "halt",
      "next": "overview"
    },
    {
      "id": "overview",
      "kind": "agent",
      "label": "guided overview + risk",
      "workflow": "overview-agent",
      "evidence": "overview.evidence.schema.json",
      "max_iterations": 2,
      "params": { "require": ["cohorts", "summary"], "non_empty": ["cohorts", "summary"] },
      "checks": [
        { "run": "evidence-present",         "on_fail": "iterate" },
        { "run": "overview-schema-valid",     "on_fail": "iterate" },
        { "run": "cohort-partition-complete", "on_fail": "iterate" }
      ],
      "conclude": "conclude-overview",
      "on_blocked": "halt",
      "next": "review"
    },
    {
      "id": "review",
      "kind": "fanout",
      "label": "multi-dimension review",
      "params": { "status_note": { "verdict_field": "verdict", "flag_verdicts": ["REQUEST_CHANGES"], "severity_field": "severity", "flag_severities": ["critical", "high"], "label": "request-changes" } },
      "branches": [
        { "id": "correctness",     "workflow": "review-correctness-agent", "evidence": "review.evidence.schema.json", "max_iterations": 2, "params": { "dimension": "correctness",     "require": ["dimension", "verdict", "findings"], "non_empty": ["dimension", "verdict"] }, "checks": [ { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-schema-valid", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-findings-anchored", "on_fail": "iterate" } ], "publish": "publish-review" },
        { "id": "test",            "workflow": "review-test-agent", "evidence": "review.evidence.schema.json", "max_iterations": 2, "params": { "dimension": "test",            "require": ["dimension", "verdict", "findings"], "non_empty": ["dimension", "verdict"] }, "checks": [ { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-schema-valid", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-findings-anchored", "on_fail": "iterate" } ], "publish": "publish-review" },
        { "id": "performance",     "workflow": "review-performance-agent", "evidence": "review.evidence.schema.json", "max_iterations": 2, "params": { "dimension": "performance",     "require": ["dimension", "verdict", "findings"], "non_empty": ["dimension", "verdict"] }, "checks": [ { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-schema-valid", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-findings-anchored", "on_fail": "iterate" } ], "publish": "publish-review" },
        { "id": "security",        "workflow": "review-security-agent", "evidence": "review.evidence.schema.json", "max_iterations": 2, "params": { "dimension": "security",        "require": ["dimension", "verdict", "findings"], "non_empty": ["dimension", "verdict"] }, "checks": [ { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-schema-valid", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-findings-anchored", "on_fail": "iterate" } ], "publish": "publish-review" },
        { "id": "maintainability", "workflow": "review-maintainability-agent", "evidence": "review.evidence.schema.json", "max_iterations": 2, "params": { "dimension": "maintainability", "require": ["dimension", "verdict", "findings"], "non_empty": ["dimension", "verdict"] }, "checks": [ { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-schema-valid", "on_fail": "iterate" }, { "run": "review-findings-anchored", "on_fail": "iterate" } ], "publish": "publish-review" }
      ],
      "next": "join-review"
    },
    { "id": "join-review", "kind": "join", "of": "review", "next": "triage" },
    {
      "id": "triage",
      "kind": "agent",
      "label": "review triage (cluster & rank)",
      "workflow": "triage-agent",
      "evidence": "triage.evidence.schema.json",
      "max_iterations": 2,
      "inputs": [
        { "from": "correctness",     "as": "correctness" },
        { "from": "test",            "as": "test" },
        { "from": "performance",     "as": "performance" },
        { "from": "security",        "as": "security" },
        { "from": "maintainability", "as": "maintainability" }
      ],
      "params": { "require": ["clusters", "summary"] },
      "checks": [
        { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" },
        { "run": "triage-schema-valid", "on_fail": "iterate" }
      ],
      "conclude": "conclude-triage",
      "next": "fix"
    },
    {
      "id": "fix",
      "kind": "agent",
      "label": "propose remediations (suggest)",
      "workflow": "fix-agent",
      "evidence": "fix.evidence.schema.json",
      "max_iterations": 2,
      "inputs": [ { "from": "triage", "as": "triage" } ],
      "params": { "require": ["fixes", "mode"] },
      "checks": [
        { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" },
        { "run": "fix-schema-valid", "on_fail": "iterate" }
      ],
      "conclude": "conclude-fix",
      "next": "post-fix"
    },
    {
      "id": "post-fix",
      "kind": "fanout",
      "label": "context capture ∥ mental-model update",
      "branches": [
        {
          "id": "context",
          "workflow": "context-agent",
          "evidence": "context.evidence.schema.json",
          "max_iterations": 2,
          "params": { "require": ["phases", "transcript_present"] },
          "checks": [
            { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "advisory" },
            { "run": "context-schema-valid", "on_fail": "advisory" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "mm",
          "states": [
            {
              "id": "mm-updater",
              "kind": "agent",
              "label": "mental-model updater",
              "workflow": "mm-updater",
              "evidence": "mm-updater.evidence.schema.json",
              "max_iterations": 2,
              "params": { "require": ["mm_changed", "rationale"] },
              "checks": [
                { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "iterate" },
                { "run": "mm-questions-present", "on_fail": "iterate" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "mm-gate",
              "kind": "gate",
              "label": "decide on the mental-model PR",
              "questions_from": "mm-updater",
              "checks": [
                { "run": "answers-coverage", "on_fail": "iterate" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "next": "join-post-fix"
    },
    { "id": "join-post-fix", "kind": "join", "of": "post-fix", "next": "mrp" },
    {
      "id": "mrp",
      "kind": "agent",
      "label": "merge-readiness pack (synthesis)",
      "workflow": "mrp-agent",
      "evidence": "mrp.evidence.schema.json",
      "max_iterations": 2,
      "inputs": [
        { "from": "preflight-gate", "as": "preflight" },
        { "from": "overview",  "as": "overview" },
        { "from": "triage",    "as": "triage" },
        { "from": "context",   "as": "context" }
      ],
      "params": { "require": ["rationale", "critique_ledger", "routed_questions", "acceptance", "acceptance_plan"] },
      "checks": [
        { "run": "evidence-present", "on_fail": "advisory" },
        { "run": "mrp-schema-valid", "on_fail": "advisory" }
      ],
      "conclude": "conclude-mrp",
      "next": "done"
    }
  ]
}
